HEADWORD: Trichotomous
<hw>Tri*chot"o*mous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Trichotomy</er>.]</ety> <def>Divided into three parts, or into
threes; three-forked; <as>as, a <ex>trichotomous</ex> stem</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Martyn.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
